Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with temporal logic and controller synthesis. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a technique for guided controller synthesis. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper discusses a framework for specifying requirements and synthesizing controllers. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method and a tool for computing controllers. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with controller synthesis and case studies are carried out to demonstrate the effectiveness of the proposed technique.
